# array-is-sorted
A small module to check if an Array is sorted.

## Example
``` javascript
import sorted from "array-is-sorted"

console.log(sorted([1, 3, 4]))
// => true

console.log(sorted([3, 2, 1], 'DESC'))
// => true

console.log(sorted({a: [1]}))
// => error
```

